parameters:
\nc<>Wait, if it's like this, is today going to end with just
volunteering!? Why did I come here in the first place?

\nc<>I totally agree. At this rate, it'll probably be next year
before we can move up to the upper floor.

\nc<>This is not the time to be talking as if it's someone
else's problem! Haven't you felt anything?

\nc<>Hmm... For now, I can't sense any aura from the other world
here. I don't know about the upper floor though.
\nc<>I guess even you are no good after all.

\nc<>Since it has come to this, I must be prepared for penalties
and use magic to infiltrate...
\nc<>Oh? Were you not talking to someone?
\nc<>Ah, ah! I was on the phone. I'm done now, so I'll go.

\nc<>Is that so? They said that the upperclassmen have other
jobs today as well.
\nc<>Since we've come this far, let's go a little further--
\nc<>Auntie, w-what is it, all of you!?

\ncHow dare you take over our workplace completely... You
guys, get them!
